<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-1a' );" name="006-1a" class="pb">[006-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　毛詩名物解卷六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:220'>　　　　　　　　　　宋　蔡　卞　集解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:225'>　釋鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='225:246'>　　　雎鳩　　鳴鳩　　黄鳥　鳲鳩　　鴻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='246:267'>　　　鷺　　　桑扈　　鶚　　鴟鴞　　隼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='267:288'>　　　鶺鴒　　鳯凰　　鵙　　䲷　　　鴟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='288:294'>　　　燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='294:320'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-1b' );" name="006-1b" class="pb">[006-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='320:326'>　　雎鳩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='326:349'>雎鳩或謂之鶚或謂之王雎凡鳩皆陽鳥也剛而能制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='349:372'>者真若乎陽故鳩訓聚而有别者也和而不同則有是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='372:395'>意故謂之雎鳩然有不可犯之道也故又謂之鶚王大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='395:418'>也於鳲鳩則爲大矣故又謂之王雎勒以法度足以一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='418:441'>衆者莫如雎鳩故雎鳩氏爲司馬夫有可歸之徳又有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='441:464'>可歸之位者后妃也故關雎又為王者之風而不爲諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='464:487'>侯之風能聚所以喻后妃之求淑女能别所以喻后妃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='487:513'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-2a' );" name="006-2a" class="pb">[006-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='513:520'>不失禮義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='520:526'>　　鳴鳩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='526:549'>鳴鳩或謂之鵲鳩或謂之鶻鵰凡名鳥者必有所善鳴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='549:572'>鳩善鳴者也春者啓之時秋者閉之時啓則有時閉則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='572:595'>無事鳴鳩以啓來而閉去故鶻鳩氏為司事臣以骨鯁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='595:618'>為任而非倡和者故命官以鶻鳩而不謂之鳴鳩也詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='618:641'>曰宛彼鳴鳩翰飛戾天非修翼之鳥而至乎其逺則敗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='641:644'>矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='644:670'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='670:676'>　　黄鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='676:699'>黄鳥之爲物中和而得時者也有中羙之性故謂之黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='699:722'>鳥其鳴以春為期其去以秋為度倉庚所以鳴其時也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='722:745'>故凡記時者皆言倉庚形色皆有中和之美黃鳥所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='745:768'>命其徳也故哀三良刺宣王皆言黄鳥仲夏黍登而聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='768:776'>伏故謂之摶黍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='776:782'>　　鳲鳩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='782:805'>鳲鳩能定志而有所守者也有所守則可以為善可以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='805:831'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-3a' );" name="006-3a" class="pb">[006-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='831:854'>爲羣故謂之鵠鶵夫王者民人之主也無均平之徳則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='854:877'>不足以治之故鳲鳩氏為司空止則在桑飛則在梅徙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='877:900'>則在棘下則在榛無往而不擇也夫人無均一之徳則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='900:923'>不足以爲諸侯之家鵲之性剛而不可奪守而不可欺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='923:946'>鳲鳩無為巢之功而有居守聚利之善此其所以得而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='946:969'>有之也是故作詩者以喻乎諸侯之夫人及其在位之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='969:992'>臣自大夫妻至庶人皆不得而擬焉蓋能一者治人非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='992:999'>治於人者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='999:1025'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-3b' );" name="006-3b" class="pb">[006-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1025:1030'>　　鴻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1030:1053'>鴻之爲物髙可以致逺卑可以濟難知時而去就者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1053:1076'>鴈不専逹而所至必從其長故大夫執鴈亦有從長之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1076:1099'>意鴈制於長成於屬有長必有屬故以鴻譬天子之使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1099:1122'>新臺云鴻則離之以長言之者詩多以山喻君而此以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1122:1145'>鴻蓋新臺之刺宣公家道也於國則言其位於家則言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1145:1168'>其長雖魚潛於卑幽鴻飛於髙逺魚網設而鴻離之豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1168:1175'>設網之意哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1175:1201'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-4a' );" name="006-4a" class="pb">[006-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1201:1206'>　　鷺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1206:1229'>鷺㓗白而不汚立常有振舉之意足常跂有振而獨舂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1229:1252'>之貌歩好自低昂而謂之獨舂也作詩者以其㓗白而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1252:1275'>不可汚喻君子之徳以常有振舉之意喻君子之威儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1275:1298'>夫威儀欲其棣棣而以振舉何也蓋不可以髙仰之驕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1298:1321'>色也不可以卑俯之俯替也是驕近亂替近疾其升也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1321:1344'>不驕其降也不替此所謂威儀棣棣不可選也然則振</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1344:1357'>鷺之威儀豈所謂髙仰者哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1357:1383'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-4b' );" name="006-4b" class="pb">[006-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1383:1389'>　　桑扈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1389:1412'>桑扈竊脂也性好集桑故因以桑則九扈之名也戸所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1412:1435'>以閉邑所以守故謂之扈羽領之間皆有文而又善自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1435:1458'>閉守故名爲扈而作詩者所以喻君子之禮文少昊氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1458:1475'>以九扈爲九農正亦曰扈民無滛者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1475:1480'>　　鴞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1480:1503'>鴞無爪牙羽翼之才而以口向物物所惡而已亦以物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1503:1526'>惡故常集於幽荒䝉蔽之土也墓門有棘有鴞萃止是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1526:1552'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1552:1575'>已泮水曰翩彼飛鴞集于泮林鴞可惡之鳥泮水可欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1575:1598'>之地且鴞之惡非翩然而集于木者惟僖公有仁厚之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1598:1621'>徳故雖所惡之鳥能集可欲之地不庭之虜猶之鴞去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1621:1644'>幽荒而集于泮林也其來雖不足以爲善惟其不害於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1644:1659'>物故能翩然集之而不為物逐也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1659:1665'>　　鴟鴞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1665:1688'>鴟鴞性隂伏而好凌物者也隂伏以時發者必有以定</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1688:1711'>之内畜志以凌物者必有以决乎外故謂之鴟鴞然其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1711:1737'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1737:1760'>害物也能竊伏而不著鷹隼之勢故鴟鴞以喻管蔡之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1760:1764'>暴亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1764:1769'>　　隼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1769:1799'>隼之擊物而必中者也必至謂之隼物而<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0616' title='KR0616' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0616.png'/>謂之鷹必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1799:1822'>至者或有所過取故作詩者以隼喻不制之諸侯而司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1822:1833'>冦之官則以鷞鳩名之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1833:1839'>　　鶺鴒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1839:1862'>鶺鴒者有所就有所招者也彼可即而即之則無不親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1862:1888'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1888:1918'>彼可令而令之則無不從如<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1799' title='KR1799' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1799.png'/>鴒之尾應首也親則有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1918:1941'>雝雝之能和從則有渠渠之能容故謂之雝渠作詩者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1941:1964'>以喻兄弟之無不親無不和也兄弟之道天性也動其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1964:1994'><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1799' title='KR1799' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1799.png'/>脅而首尾應者雖有强誠亦自然而已故字或以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1994:1998'>鶺鴒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1998:2004'>　　鳯凰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2004:2027'>瑞應者也盛徳之所感天命之所受則應時而至矣少</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2027:2050'>昊氏以鳥名官而鳯凰為歴正分至啓閉之官皆有屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2050:2076'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-6b' );" name="006-6b" class="pb">[006-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2076:2099'>焉故詩以喻大臣鳯凰鳴矣于彼髙岡者朝廷也鳴者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2099:2117'>辟令也蓋國有六職有坐者而論道者焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2117:2122'>　　鵙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2122:2145'>鵙見於萬物開閤之時夏至而鳴冬至而止天地不勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2145:2168'>萬物以生萬物以死夏至則生者勞物冬至則死者定</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2168:2191'>物鵙鳴同萬物而勞者也故謂之百勞鳴於二至之間</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2191:2214'>故伯趙為司至七月以鵙為將續之候觀天時而終人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2214:2226'>事所以順萬物而作者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2226:2252'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-7a' );" name="006-7a" class="pb">[006-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2252:2257'>　　梟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2257:2280'>梟類鴟而尤好陵物者也有陵物之意故當求之端待</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2280:2303'>發氣果敢而發必中聲當曉者以其如此非若强茅之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2303:2308'>隂伏也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2308:2313'>　　鴟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2313:2336'>鴟猛而不剛勇而無才塞而不通故謂之强茅從大而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2336:2359'>不能有為故謂之鴟哲婦之主乎内也其為物若梟其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2359:2375'>隂伏若鴟故曰懿厥哲婦爲梟為鴟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2375:2401'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-7b' );" name="006-7b" class="pb">[006-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2401:2406'>　　燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2406:2429'>燕就陽而畏隂南北徃來有生息之道知天時而不違</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2429:2453'>以自飬至南而勞至北而息勞而生也息所歸也𤣥鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2453:2477'>西北乙鳥東南自所歸而言故謂之𤣥鳥自所生而言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2477:2500'>故謂之乙鳥或就所生而言或就所歸而言何也蓋官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2500:2524'>之親就天道而司人事歸以息者天道𤣥者天之成象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2524:2549'>也故司分為𤣥鳥氏𤣥者氣之自然而正也故以天道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2549:2573'>言之則配以自成天命𤣥鳥降而生商非人之所為也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2573:2599'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '006-8a' );" name="006-8a" class="pb">[006-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2599:2622'>燕之生育於東北蓋人所見也故謂之乙其來去有自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2622:2645'>安之道故謂之燕莊姜送歸妾而謂之燕燕于飛雖以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2645:2657'>為燕而亦有自安之道歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2657:2660'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2660:2663'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2663:2666'>　</span><br/>
